{"type":"message","id":"f402d771","parentId":"10f4e73a","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:31:46.699Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have successfully created a complete React + TypeScript + Vite project for the OpenClaw Control Center. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## Project Structure Created\n\n```\ncontrol-center/\n├── index.html              # HTML entry with dark theme by default\n├── package.json            # Dependencies and scripts\n├── tailwind.config.js      # Tailwind CSS configuration with dark theme colors\n├── tsconfig.json           # TypeScript configuration\n├── tsconfig.node.json      # TypeScript config for Node\n├── vite.config.ts          # Vite configuration\n└── src/\n    ├── main.tsx            # React entry point\n    ├── App.tsx             # Main app with sidebar navigation\n    ├── index.css           # Tailwind directives and CSS variables\n    ├── vite-env.d.ts       # Vite type declarations\n    └── pages/\n        ├── Dashboard.tsx   # 总览 - Overview with charts and stats\n        ├── Agents.tsx      # 员工 - AI Agents management\n        ├── Memory.tsx      # 记忆 - Memory/data management\n        ├── Documents.tsx   # 文档 - Document management\n        ├── Usage.tsx       # 用量 - Usage analytics and charts\n        ├── Tasks.tsx       # 任务 - Task management\n        └── Settings.tsx    # 设置 - Settings panel\n```\n\n## Features Implemented\n\n1. **Navigation Sidebar** - 7 navigation items with bilingual labels (Chinese/English)\n2. **Dark Theme by Default** - Professional dark UI with Tailwind CSS\n3. **Dashboard** - Stats cards, area charts, bar charts, active agents list, quick actions\n4. **Agents Page** - Agent cards with status, capabilities, progress bars\n5. **Memory Page** - Memory entries list with search, categories, tags\n6. **Documents Page** - File browser with list/grid views, folders sidebar\n7. **Usage Page** - Usage statistics, charts, model distribution, alerts\n8. **Tasks Page** - Task list with status, priority, progress tracking\n9. **Settings Page** - Profile, notifications, security, appearance settings\n\n## To Run the Project\n\n```bash\ncd C:/Users/Administrator/.openclaw/workspace/control-center\nnpm install\nnpm run dev\n```\n\nThe project uses:\n- **React 18** with TypeScript\n- **Vite** for fast development\n- **Tailwind CSS** for styling\n- **React Router** for navigation\n- **Lucide React** for icons\n- **Recharts** for data visualization\n- **date-fns** for date formatting"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":305,"output":522,"cacheRead":64000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64827,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773761477189}}
